text: Kamina is a Telugu language film directed by Lakshmikanth Chenna and featuring Sai Kumar, Roja, Krishi Arimanda, Brahmaji, Ravi Babu, Ashish Vidyarthi and Lekha Washington in important roles. It is the Telugu remake of the 2007 Bollywood film Johnny Gaddar. ==References== Category:2010s Telugu-language films Category:Films shot in Telangana Category:Films shot in Vijayawada Category:Films shot in Bangalore Category:Films set in Hyderabad, India Category:Films set in Vijayawada Category:Films set in Bangalore
